## Skipping Validations

```ruby
# Save without validations (use with caution!)
article.save(validate: false)

# Update without validations
article.update_attribute(:title, "New Title")  # Skips validations
article.update_column(:title, "New Title")     # Skips validations and callbacks

# Methods that skip validations:
# - update_attribute
# - update_column
# - update_columns
# - increment!
# - decrement!
# - touch
# - save(validate: false)
```

